WEBVTT

00:00:35.970 --> 00:00:38.640
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.220
=Episode 24=

00:00:44.833 --> 00:00:45.791
Spare me!

00:00:46.166 --> 00:00:48.125
Don't kill my wife and children!

00:00:48.541 --> 00:00:49.625
Spare me!

00:00:51.666 --> 00:00:52.625
Spare me!

00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:55.875
Advisor Dong, you are
the phantom thief Feng Fuliu?

00:00:56.458 --> 00:00:57.291
Stop crying!

00:00:57.875 --> 00:00:59.500
Tell me what happened.

00:00:59.666 --> 00:01:00.333
That is impossible.

00:01:00.833 --> 00:01:03.291
Feng Fuliu took my wife
and children hostage.

00:01:03.833 --> 00:01:06.291
He made me pretend to be you
in the main hall,

00:01:06.541 --> 00:01:08.291
then disguised himself as you
and escaped.

00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:11.291
He said he would kill my family
if I refused.

00:01:14.416 --> 00:01:15.416
I have treated you well
all these years.

00:01:15.916 --> 00:01:17.125
Tell me everything clearly,

00:01:17.291 --> 00:01:18.000
and I will spare your life.

00:01:25.916 --> 00:01:26.291
You...

00:01:28.208 --> 00:01:29.083
I will borrow this for a few days.

00:01:34.750 --> 00:01:35.375
Advisor Dong.

00:01:36.041 --> 00:01:36.833
Your wife and children are fine.

00:01:36.833 --> 00:01:37.458
Over there!

00:01:37.833 --> 00:01:40.083
They only went back to her parents' home
after your fight.

00:01:41.375 --> 00:01:42.166
Thank you!

00:01:42.416 --> 00:01:43.541
Thank you!

00:01:44.708 --> 00:01:45.458
Thank you!

00:01:48.541 --> 00:01:50.416
What did Feng Fuliu say to you
just now?

00:01:50.916 --> 00:01:51.958
He stole the jade.

00:01:54.375 --> 00:01:55.000
After him!

00:01:55.250 --> 00:01:56.250
- Go!
- Hurry!

00:01:58.666 --> 00:01:59.083
Xintian.

00:01:59.291 --> 00:02:00.833
You and Hua find a way
to stall Mr. Lu.

00:02:01.125 --> 00:02:02.166
I will go meet Feng Fuliu.

00:02:02.166 --> 00:02:02.833
Wait for my signal arrow.

00:02:03.541 --> 00:02:04.166
Don't move.

00:02:06.083 --> 00:02:06.541
Gao Quan.

00:02:06.666 --> 00:02:07.500
Take a squad that way.

00:02:07.833 --> 00:02:08.625
The rest, with me.

00:02:08.750 --> 00:02:09.333
Yes, my lord.

00:02:09.666 --> 00:02:10.166
Move!

00:02:10.500 --> 00:02:11.000
Go!

00:02:13.208 --> 00:02:14.916
Mr. Lu, Feng Fuliu seems
to be this way.

00:02:15.041 --> 00:02:16.375
No, that way.

00:02:17.708 --> 00:02:18.125
Stop.

00:02:21.541 --> 00:02:22.750
Did either of you see clearly?

00:02:22.916 --> 00:02:24.041
Which way did Feng Fuliu go?

00:02:24.041 --> 00:02:24.583
That way.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:25.708
This way.

00:02:25.875 --> 00:02:26.416
Zuo Da. Jiang Biao.

00:02:26.583 --> 00:02:26.875
Yes.

00:02:27.041 --> 00:02:27.166
Yes.

00:02:27.166 --> 00:02:27.708
Each of you takes a team.

00:02:27.958 --> 00:02:28.750
Search the whole city.

00:02:29.041 --> 00:02:29.333
Yes!

00:02:29.333 --> 00:02:29.791
Everyone.

00:02:29.791 --> 00:02:30.083
That way.

00:02:30.083 --> 00:02:30.625
Come with me.

00:02:30.833 --> 00:02:31.333
Yes.

00:02:31.833 --> 00:02:32.500
Go.

00:02:38.916 --> 00:02:40.333
Do you think the person
behind Leng Xin

00:02:40.791 --> 00:02:42.083
is a high official at court?

00:02:42.208 --> 00:02:42.958
Why are you here?

00:02:48.458 --> 00:02:50.000
While you were all fighting,

00:02:51.250 --> 00:02:52.250
I came here to wait for you.

00:02:55.208 --> 00:02:56.125
How did you know

00:02:56.708 --> 00:02:58.291
I would come to this flower pavilion?

00:03:00.458 --> 00:03:01.208
Because...

00:03:02.291 --> 00:03:02.833
Because

00:03:04.208 --> 00:03:06.041
this is where we first met.

00:03:10.625 --> 00:03:12.208
Yes and no.

00:03:13.333 --> 00:03:14.500
So I took a gamble.

00:03:14.875 --> 00:03:15.500
Then congratulations.

00:03:16.916 --> 00:03:17.500
You won.

00:03:21.166 --> 00:03:22.791
We know you are full of tricks.

00:03:24.083 --> 00:03:26.208
Catching you inside
the Northern Bureau would be difficult.

00:03:26.458 --> 00:03:28.291
So we pretended your plan had worked

00:03:28.916 --> 00:03:29.875
and let you drop your guard.

00:03:31.166 --> 00:03:33.166
This is one of your many hideouts.

00:03:34.541 --> 00:03:36.041
So I came here first and waited.

00:03:36.125 --> 00:03:36.666
Miss Shen.

00:03:37.625 --> 00:03:38.500
You have gotten smarter.

00:03:38.750 --> 00:03:39.375
To beat you,

00:03:40.375 --> 00:03:41.666
I have to be a little cunning.

00:03:42.333 --> 00:03:43.333
You came alone,

00:03:44.791 --> 00:03:45.708
without a squad of men.

00:03:48.958 --> 00:03:50.125
You have something to ask me.

00:03:51.708 --> 00:03:52.666
Hua and Xintian

00:03:53.166 --> 00:03:54.791
are circling nearby with our men.

00:03:55.541 --> 00:03:56.875
Once I fire the signal arrow,

00:03:57.583 --> 00:03:58.583
they will come at once.

00:03:59.750 --> 00:04:01.916
You move through the manors
of nobles and officials,

00:04:02.416 --> 00:04:03.333
stealing treasures.

00:04:03.958 --> 00:04:05.250
Does it have something to do
with Leng Xin?

00:04:10.291 --> 00:04:11.375
You are investigating Leng Xin too?

00:04:12.916 --> 00:04:14.166
Are you doing it by order,

00:04:15.083 --> 00:04:16.500
or do you have a grudge against him?

00:04:21.041 --> 00:04:21.416
Well...

00:04:24.041 --> 00:04:24.875
I cannot tell you.

00:04:26.875 --> 00:04:27.291
Fine.

00:04:28.708 --> 00:04:30.125
Then what clues

00:04:30.375 --> 00:04:31.458
can you share with me?

00:04:31.625 --> 00:04:32.541
I found out

00:04:33.416 --> 00:04:34.291
that Leng Xin answers

00:04:34.958 --> 00:04:35.875
to an imperial jade.

00:04:37.125 --> 00:04:39.458
But our dynasty has lasted generations
since the Founding Emperor,

00:04:40.750 --> 00:04:43.166
and far too many gifts have been granted
to nobles and officials.

00:04:43.375 --> 00:04:44.375
I haven't been able to trace

00:04:44.375 --> 00:04:45.625
the exact origin of this jade.

00:04:46.500 --> 00:04:47.208
So...

00:04:48.083 --> 00:04:49.625
So you steal treasures,

00:04:49.916 --> 00:04:52.041
and if they are not the one,
you return them.

00:04:53.375 --> 00:04:54.166
Correct.

00:04:54.375 --> 00:04:55.250
Why go that far?

00:04:58.375 --> 00:04:59.375
If I told you

00:05:00.375 --> 00:05:01.208
that taking down Leng Xin

00:05:02.375 --> 00:05:03.375
would make me

00:05:04.041 --> 00:05:05.125
number one on the Bounty List,

00:05:05.625 --> 00:05:06.416
would you believe me?

00:05:06.625 --> 00:05:07.166
Fine.

00:05:08.916 --> 00:05:10.291
Then one last question.

00:05:11.750 --> 00:05:12.333
Yes?

00:05:12.833 --> 00:05:13.583
Five years ago,

00:05:15.041 --> 00:05:16.375
were you the one

00:05:16.375 --> 00:05:17.583
who saved me from the Iron-Blooded
Three Eagles?

00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:50.430
♪Lost too deep in the haze,
my eyes turn red♪

00:05:50.720 --> 00:05:56.560
♪Your scent remains
and walks with me♪

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:58.125
Was it you or not?

00:06:05.291 --> 00:06:06.166
If I say yes,

00:06:07.708 --> 00:06:08.958
will you let me go?

00:06:19.333 --> 00:06:20.458
That's my choice to make.

00:06:21.083 --> 00:06:22.708
I just want to know if it was you.

00:06:28.666 --> 00:06:29.958
You should take me in.

00:06:41.875 --> 00:06:43.333
Another fork?

00:06:44.750 --> 00:06:45.541
That way.

00:06:45.750 --> 00:06:46.208
Yes.

00:06:46.583 --> 00:06:46.958
Come with me.

00:06:47.250 --> 00:06:48.250
- Fei.
- Yes.

00:06:48.333 --> 00:06:49.166
Take two men and check it out.

00:06:49.458 --> 00:06:49.791
Go.

00:06:51.625 --> 00:06:52.583
Are you leading me

00:06:52.583 --> 00:06:53.666
around in circles?

00:06:54.666 --> 00:06:56.041
Every time we reach a fork,
you split our men.

00:06:56.041 --> 00:06:57.208
Are you stalling on purpose,

00:06:57.208 --> 00:06:59.291
or helping Feng Fuliu

00:06:59.500 --> 00:07:00.500
escape the chase?

00:07:01.708 --> 00:07:03.291
The fewer men I have left,

00:07:03.833 --> 00:07:05.000
the easier it is

00:07:05.375 --> 00:07:06.250
for your little schemes to work.

00:07:08.125 --> 00:07:09.291
I remember now.

00:07:09.666 --> 00:07:10.500
Feng Fuliu

00:07:11.208 --> 00:07:13.875
seemed to go that way.

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:14.583
That way?

00:07:15.458 --> 00:07:16.583
Listen carefully.

00:07:17.666 --> 00:07:18.375
At dawn,

00:07:19.041 --> 00:07:20.333
the three-day deadline is up.

00:07:20.500 --> 00:07:21.416
If Feng Fuliu is not caught,

00:07:21.750 --> 00:07:23.625
I'm guilty of negligence at worst.

00:07:23.625 --> 00:07:25.291
But you will lose your heads.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:28.250
So don't lie to me again.

00:07:28.916 --> 00:07:29.625
No, no.

00:07:30.125 --> 00:07:31.541
I remember now.

00:07:31.750 --> 00:07:33.583
Mr. Lu, he ran that way.

00:07:33.833 --> 00:07:34.375
Go.

00:07:38.125 --> 00:07:38.625
What?

00:07:40.166 --> 00:07:41.958
The greatest female bounty hunter

00:07:45.375 --> 00:07:46.125
is hesitating?

00:07:49.666 --> 00:07:50.416
I will not run anymore.

00:07:52.208 --> 00:07:52.791
Take me in.

00:08:04.333 --> 00:08:05.166
Is this another trick?

00:08:09.833 --> 00:08:10.375
No tricks left.

00:08:16.208 --> 00:08:16.750
Tonight,

00:08:19.458 --> 00:08:20.416
I lost to you.

00:08:25.916 --> 00:08:26.625
What?

00:08:28.458 --> 00:08:29.666
Why are you panicking?

00:08:34.916 --> 00:08:36.250
You must be plotting something.

00:08:37.833 --> 00:08:39.000
You can't bear to arrest me.

00:08:40.208 --> 00:08:41.083
That is not true.

00:08:52.541 --> 00:08:53.416
Who sent you to kill me?

00:09:07.083 --> 00:09:07.916
A signal arrow went up over there.

00:09:08.333 --> 00:09:08.750
Right.

00:09:09.375 --> 00:09:10.583
Feng Fuliu may be that way.

00:09:11.291 --> 00:09:11.666
Go.

00:09:12.750 --> 00:09:13.041
Go.

00:09:13.125 --> 00:09:14.625
Find the main force. Hurry!

00:09:14.750 --> 00:09:15.083
Go.

00:09:15.500 --> 00:09:15.791
Yes.

00:10:07.833 --> 00:10:08.625
It's Feng Fuliu.

00:10:09.333 --> 00:10:10.291
Loose arrows. Burn him!

00:10:34.041 --> 00:10:34.625
Mr. Lu!

00:10:34.708 --> 00:10:35.875
Bingfan is still inside.

00:10:35.916 --> 00:10:36.583
Mr. Lu!

00:10:36.750 --> 00:10:37.291
What?

00:10:37.541 --> 00:10:38.625
Shen Bingfan is inside?

00:10:39.166 --> 00:10:40.291
Mr. Guan, don't go.
It is too dangerous!

00:10:40.291 --> 00:10:40.625
Constable Guan!

00:10:40.625 --> 00:10:41.125
Let me go!

00:10:41.208 --> 00:10:41.708
Constable Guan!

00:10:41.750 --> 00:10:43.000
Let me go!

00:10:46.916 --> 00:10:48.750
I didn't expect it to end like this.

00:10:50.875 --> 00:10:52.083
You look beautiful when you smile.

00:10:54.083 --> 00:10:55.250
Don't miss me too much.

00:11:33.250 --> 00:11:33.791
Bingfan!

00:11:33.791 --> 00:11:34.541
Bingfan!

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:35.666
Bingfan!

00:11:40.500 --> 00:11:44.125
Put out the fire! Hurry!

00:11:44.125 --> 00:11:44.916
No!

00:11:44.916 --> 00:11:46.000
Burn Feng Fuliu to death!

00:11:49.250 --> 00:11:50.041
Mr. Lu.

00:11:50.166 --> 00:11:51.333
The Twin Dragon Jade is still
on Feng Fuliu.

00:11:51.625 --> 00:11:52.708
If it burns, we can't explain it.

00:11:53.791 --> 00:11:55.458
Put out the fire! Hurry!

00:11:55.541 --> 00:11:55.958
Put it out!

00:11:55.958 --> 00:11:56.375
Yes.

00:11:56.583 --> 00:11:57.375
Put out the fire!

00:11:57.541 --> 00:11:57.875
Hurry!

00:11:59.375 --> 00:12:00.708
Hurry. Over there!

00:12:01.708 --> 00:12:02.125
Hurry!

00:12:05.125 --> 00:12:05.750
Hurry!

00:12:27.375 --> 00:12:28.083
Come on!

00:12:38.500 --> 00:12:39.583
Where is this place?

00:13:06.708 --> 00:13:07.333
Found it.

00:13:11.583 --> 00:13:12.541
It's the Twin Dragon Jade.

00:13:13.458 --> 00:13:14.541
It's undamaged.

00:13:16.208 --> 00:13:17.166
That's all that matters.

00:13:18.750 --> 00:13:19.291
My lord.

00:13:20.166 --> 00:13:21.500
We didn't find Feng Fuliu's body.

00:13:21.958 --> 00:13:22.666
No matter.

00:13:23.125 --> 00:13:23.791
Jinyiwei.

00:13:24.333 --> 00:13:24.708
Leave!

00:13:25.208 --> 00:13:25.583
Yes!

00:13:25.833 --> 00:13:26.208
Go!

00:13:36.500 --> 00:13:38.666
Chang Beiming! Open the door!

00:13:39.125 --> 00:13:40.166
Chang Beiming! Open up!

00:13:40.833 --> 00:13:41.583
Chang Beiming!

00:13:42.458 --> 00:13:43.208
Chang Beiming!

00:13:43.916 --> 00:13:45.041
Don't play this kind of joke on me.

00:13:45.375 --> 00:13:46.125
Enough.

00:13:46.458 --> 00:13:47.958
You have been banging on the door
all morning.

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:49.125
Can I get some sleep?

00:13:50.125 --> 00:13:51.666
Chang Huan, where is your master?

00:13:52.458 --> 00:13:54.333
My master went out yesterday evening

00:13:54.666 --> 00:13:55.833
and never came back.

00:14:01.890 --> 00:14:06.600
♪In a fleeting moment♪

00:14:07.850 --> 00:14:12.150
♪Whose face crosses my mind♪

00:14:14.400 --> 00:14:19.190
♪Whose name is it♪

00:14:20.310 --> 00:14:24.560
♪I whisper in my heart♪

00:14:25.390 --> 00:14:32.020
♪Yet in the crowd, we brush past♪

00:14:32.600 --> 00:14:35.640
♪Only then did I understand fate♪

00:14:35.640 --> 00:14:39.140
♪Was hidden in the day we met♪

00:14:40.180 --> 00:14:44.470
♪A fate that cannot be severed♪

00:14:44.470 --> 00:14:46.680
♪Round and round♪

00:14:47.180 --> 00:14:51.520
♪Threads of love bind us together♪

00:14:51.520 --> 00:14:55.890
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

00:14:57.680 --> 00:15:03.970
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

00:15:03.970 --> 00:15:07.720
♪This longing I cannot say♪

00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:13.020
♪I wish you could hear♪

00:15:37.680 --> 00:15:42.020
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

00:15:43.770 --> 00:15:50.520
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

00:15:50.890 --> 00:15:54.140
♪This longing I cannot say♪

00:15:54.140 --> 00:16:01.040
♪Tucked away inside my heart♪

00:16:02.100 --> 00:16:06.720
♪Afraid love will fade like smoke♪

00:16:08.390 --> 00:16:15.290
♪Afraid memories will fade like dreams♪

00:16:15.520 --> 00:16:18.890
♪This longing I cannot say♪

00:16:19.250 --> 00:16:20.000
You scumbag.

00:16:20.166 --> 00:16:21.250
Where did you go?

00:16:21.791 --> 00:16:22.833
Why are you cursing me?

00:16:23.333 --> 00:16:25.291
I will do more than curse you.
I will beat you up.

00:16:26.833 --> 00:16:28.000
You were gone all night

00:16:28.333 --> 00:16:30.583
and vanished without a word.

00:16:30.666 --> 00:16:32.083
Do you know how worried we were?

00:16:33.333 --> 00:16:34.583
Listen to me, Chang.

00:16:35.166 --> 00:16:36.541
If you ever stay out all night again,

00:16:36.583 --> 00:16:37.666
see what I do to you.

00:16:37.666 --> 00:16:38.250
Shh.

00:16:38.541 --> 00:16:39.458
Don't shush me.

00:16:42.083 --> 00:16:43.375
Where exactly were you last night?

00:16:43.625 --> 00:16:45.250
Did you go drinking, gambling,

00:16:45.250 --> 00:16:46.208
or chasing women?

00:16:51.791 --> 00:16:54.250
He was with me last night.

00:16:55.458 --> 00:16:56.125
Who are you?

00:16:58.500 --> 00:16:59.125
My mother.

00:17:01.333 --> 00:17:02.916
First-Rank Lady
of Duke Zheng's Manor.

00:17:03.208 --> 00:17:03.875
My mother.

00:17:16.791 --> 00:17:17.750
It is all right. Come here.

00:17:26.416 --> 00:17:26.875
Mother.

00:17:27.500 --> 00:17:28.333
This is Bingfan.

00:17:29.875 --> 00:17:31.958
Shen Bingfan greets Your Ladyship.

00:17:35.166 --> 00:17:36.250
Shen Bingfan.

00:17:38.625 --> 00:17:39.375
Come inside.

00:17:40.291 --> 00:17:41.291
Let's talk.

00:17:42.625 --> 00:17:44.833
Mother, I will take her
to wash her face.

00:17:53.333 --> 00:17:53.666
My lord.

00:17:53.958 --> 00:17:55.750
Yesterday, I personally
commanded the operation

00:17:56.166 --> 00:17:57.000
and used the jade as bait.

00:17:57.083 --> 00:17:58.625
I drove Feng Fuliu into a dead end

00:17:58.625 --> 00:17:59.333
until he threw himself into the fire.

00:17:59.791 --> 00:18:00.791
The Twin Dragon Jade is unharmed.

00:18:00.791 --> 00:18:01.583
The phantom thief has been brought
to justice,

00:18:01.583 --> 00:18:02.458
and we also severely wounded

00:18:02.458 --> 00:18:04.083
Leng Xin, the top fugitive
on the Bounty List.

00:18:04.875 --> 00:18:05.333
With this victory,

00:18:05.666 --> 00:18:07.500
the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau
will be known throughout the land.

00:18:07.833 --> 00:18:09.583
All thanks to His Majesty's grace

00:18:09.916 --> 00:18:12.041
and your great fortune, my lord.

00:18:24.958 --> 00:18:25.708
Guokai.

00:18:26.333 --> 00:18:28.833
You commanded last night's operation?

00:18:29.375 --> 00:18:30.375
Yes, my lord.

00:18:30.625 --> 00:18:33.625
I will be sure to recommend you
for a reward.

00:18:49.310 --> 00:18:52.480
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:52.850 --> 00:18:56.230
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:56.480 --> 00:18:59.480
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:02.890
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:19:03.980 --> 00:19:07.190
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:07.600 --> 00:19:10.940
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:11.520 --> 00:19:13.730
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:13.730 --> 00:19:17.770
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:17.770 --> 00:19:21.640
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:21.640 --> 00:19:25.390
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:25.690 --> 00:19:27.600
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:27.600 --> 00:19:32.140
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:32.440 --> 00:19:33.940
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:33.940 --> 00:19:36.310
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:36.310 --> 00:19:40.190
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:40.190 --> 00:19:42.520
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:42.520 --> 00:19:47.520
♪And run toward this vast life♪